This directory contains source code to Lemon, a LALR parser generator
for C and D languages.

To compile the project, run:

    ./configure			-- Run the configure script
    make			-- Run the makefile.
    make install		-- (Optional) Install the build products

Additional information:

    https://github.com/sergev/lemon-parser-generator/wiki
    http://freshmeat.net/articles/view/1270/
    http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lemon_Parser
